### Public menu list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc

### Public COFFEE menu list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus?category=COFFEE&status=ON_SALE&page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc

### Public menu detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus/{{seedAmericanoMenuId}}

### Popular menu before/after orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menus/popular

